# ==============================================================================
# RESTORE INSTRUCTIONS
# ==============================================================================
# When restoring a site:
# 1. Clone this repo
# 2. Create missing directories: mkdir -p wp-content/uploads
# 3. Download third-party plugins from production (wp-content/plugins/)
# 4. Download third-party themes from production (wp-content/themes/)
# 5. Import database backup
# 6. Update wp-config.php with local database credentials
#
# CUSTOM PLUGINS/THEMES:
# - Replace "my-custom-plugin" and "my-custom-theme" with your actual names
# - These will be version controlled automatically
# - Third-party plugins/themes are ignored (download separately)